---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Public Safety & Resilience - APSU GIS Center" description="Geospatial solutions for emergency management, hazard mitigation, and facility resilience.">
  <section class="bs-container py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="bs-h1 mb-6 text-apsu-red">Public Safety & Facility Resilience</h1>
      <p class="bs-body-text text-xl mb-12">
        We partner with local and regional agencies to provide data-driven insights for emergency response and hazard mitigation.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="bg-bs-surface-2 p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h2 class="bs-h3 mb-4">Emergency Management</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-bs-foreground-dark">
            Our team develops real-time dashboards and mapping applications that assist first responders and emergency managers in situational awareness.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-bs-foreground-light">
            <li>Incident Mapping</li>
            <li>Resource Allocation</li>
            <li>Hazard Analysis</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bs-surface-2 p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h2 class="bs-h3 mb-4">Facility Resilience</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-bs-foreground-dark">
            We map and analyze critical infrastructure to ensure continuity of operations during disruptions.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-bs-foreground-light">
            <li>Indoor Mapping</li>
            <li>Utility Network Analysis</li>
            <li>Asset Management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
